  \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/valve-steam-machine-with-the-valve-logo-above-and-the-steam-logo-on-the-sides.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/valve-steam-machine-with-the-valve-logo-above-and-the-steam-logo-on-the-sides.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/valve-steam-machine-with-the-valve-logo-above-and-the-steam-logo-on-the-sides.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/valve-steam-machine-with-the-valve-logo-above-and-the-steam-logo-on-the-sides.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/valve-steam-machine-with-the-valve-logo-above-and-the-steam-logo-on-the-sides.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/valve-steam-machine-with-the-valve-logo-above-and-the-steam-logo-on-the-sides.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Valve Steam Machine with the Valve logo above and the Steam logo on the sides.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/valve-steam-machine-with-the-valve-logo-above-and-the-steam-logo-on-the-sides.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/valve-steam-machine-with-the-valve-logo-above-and-the-steam-logo-on-the-sides.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"the-xbox-console-is-clearly-not-the-center-of-the-xbox-universe-anymore\"\u003e\n                        The Xbox Console Is Clearly Not the Center of the Xbox Universe Anymore\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Xbox-branded ROG handheld and new Windows 11 experience isn\u0026#39;t really just about handheld gaming. This is just the tip of the iceberg and, in my opinion, the first look at a broader strategy to diffuse Xbox over all platforms, and move the resource drain of native hardware development out into the general PC hardware space.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"3964-45a7-a927e5c825c1\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.howtogeek.com/xbox-is-now-the-betamax-of-gaming-consoles/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"An Xbox Series X and Betamax tape on a vintage media.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/an-xbox-series-x-and-betamax-tape-on-a-vintage-media.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis was exactly Microsoft\u0026#39;s recipe for success when it created DOS for the IBM PC and its subsequent clones. As opposed to its rival at the time, Apple, which has been a computer hardware company from day one. Rarely has a Microsoft foray into hardware been a success, and the company\u0026#39;s strength is in software and services.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eRight now, Microsoft claims that a next-generation of Xbox hardware is still coming, but if this experiment with the ROG handheld works out, who\u0026#39;s to say that the next \u0026#34;Xbox\u0026#34; isn\u0026#39;t just a regular PC with this modified version of Windows?\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
